Definition:

Second term: old
Positive Examples.explanation: It is True since "internet" is made of "old".

Positive Examples.input:

Second term: goat sucker
Positive Examples.explanation: It is False since "president" is not made of "goat sucker".

Negative Examples.input:

Second term: very large country
Negative Examples.explanation: It is False since "brazil" is not made of "very large country". Hence, output "Yes" is incorrect.

Negative Examples.input:
First term: toy 
Second term: platic
Negative Examples.explanation: It is True since "toy" is made of "platic". Hence, output "No" is incorrect.
